WEBVTT

00:01:34.397 --> 00:01:38.071
Water… Oh, yeah.
That's where you wanna go.

00:01:39.073 --> 00:01:41.578
If you head just a little way's
past that elevated track,

00:01:41.662 --> 00:01:43.624
there's an underground passage.

00:01:43.707 --> 00:01:45.586
Water builds up there all the time.

00:01:45.670 --> 00:01:48.383
[Kiruko] Sweet, thanks.
We'll head over there.

00:01:48.466 --> 00:01:51.682
Uh, wait! Don't you guys need
somewhere to rest first?

00:01:51.765 --> 00:01:54.896
We've got the cleanest rooms,
and the freshest futons in town.

00:01:54.980 --> 00:01:55.982
Come on.

00:01:56.567 --> 00:01:58.904
Sorry, but we don't really have time
to hang around.

00:01:59.488 --> 00:02:00.658
Uh-- Oh.

00:02:01.367 --> 00:02:02.787
Right, of course.

00:02:04.541 --> 00:02:05.668
Although,

00:02:05.751 --> 00:02:07.672
I guess if we're heading to get water,

00:02:07.755 --> 00:02:10.427
it wouldn't hurt to leave our bags
somewhere for a while.

00:02:10.511 --> 00:02:12.557
With any luck,
we'll have a lot of water to haul.

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:14.059
[laughs]

00:02:15.855 --> 00:02:17.859
[Maru] You totally just did that
to give her money.

00:02:18.778 --> 00:02:21.992
You're too nice.
What if she tries to rob us?

00:02:22.075 --> 00:02:24.706
Well, she'd be out of luck,
'cause we are broke.

00:02:25.290 --> 00:02:28.171
She told us to keep our valuables
with us, right?

00:02:28.254 --> 00:02:29.340
We can trust her.

00:02:29.423 --> 00:02:31.052
<i>You know, probably.</i>

00:02:32.931 --> 00:02:34.225
[Maru] Oh, hey! Look!

00:02:35.352 --> 00:02:37.272
You think that's our underground passage?

00:02:42.449 --> 00:02:43.702
[Maru grunts]

00:02:49.589 --> 00:02:51.425
[water dripping]

00:02:51.510 --> 00:02:52.512
[gasps]

00:02:56.227 --> 00:02:57.605
Run off.

00:02:57.689 --> 00:03:00.987
There could be all kinds of nasty bacteria
living in there.

00:03:01.070 --> 00:03:03.408
Not exactly safe for us to drink.

00:03:08.459 --> 00:03:09.796
There's someone over there!

00:03:09.880 --> 00:03:12.175
Hey, get out of there! The bacteria!

00:03:12.886 --> 00:03:13.888
[sighs]

00:03:19.858 --> 00:03:21.528
[groans]

00:03:27.999 --> 00:03:29.919
Guy's in pretty bad shape.

00:03:30.003 --> 00:03:31.380
Is he still alive?

00:03:31.464 --> 00:03:32.967
[stranger] My friend…

00:03:33.051 --> 00:03:34.846
Please, you gotta help him.

00:03:36.015 --> 00:03:37.685
It was a monster.

00:03:38.227 --> 00:03:39.648
Damn thing got him.

00:03:40.398 --> 00:03:41.442
I'm begging you.

00:03:42.235 --> 00:03:43.321
Leave.

00:04:03.821 --> 00:04:05.741
Oh, man.
I think his friend's already a goner.

00:04:05.825 --> 00:04:07.285
-Sis, look.
-[gasps]

00:04:10.083 --> 00:04:12.170
-[gasps]
-[howling]

00:04:15.553 --> 00:04:16.555
Let's go!

00:04:48.409 --> 00:04:49.954
[Maru whimpers]

00:05:00.601 --> 00:05:02.437
-Boom goes the dynamite.
-Huh?

00:05:03.481 --> 00:05:07.740
[Kiruko] Don't love that I had to squander
a bullet on him, but look.

00:05:07.824 --> 00:05:08.826
He's done for.

00:05:09.409 --> 00:05:10.411
Whoa!

00:05:10.495 --> 00:05:12.583
Once you know something's
gonna chase after you,

00:05:12.667 --> 00:05:14.002
setting up a trap's easy.

00:05:14.086 --> 00:05:17.175
[Maru] It's crazy how fast
you come up with this stuff.

00:05:17.259 --> 00:05:18.469
[Kiruko chuckles]

00:05:19.471 --> 00:05:21.475
You're up, Maru. Go do your thing.

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:22.854
Oh, uh-- Right.

00:05:23.354 --> 00:05:24.774
Okay…

00:05:26.235 --> 00:05:27.989
Fatal Dive!

00:05:28.072 --> 00:05:33.709
[echoing]
<i>Fatal Dive! Fatal Dive! Fatal Dive!</i>

00:05:38.176 --> 00:05:39.261
Huh?

00:05:39.344 --> 00:05:40.346
Hmm?

00:05:40.848 --> 00:05:42.100
[soft howl]

00:05:43.060 --> 00:05:44.062
Uh-oh.

00:05:45.190 --> 00:05:47.485
[Maru] It's not a Hiruko, it's an animal!

00:05:47.570 --> 00:05:49.323
-[Kiruko] Wait, are you serious?
-[Maru] Run, run!

00:05:49.406 --> 00:05:50.868
-[Kiruko] Okay. Maru, over here!
-[Maru] Run!

00:05:50.951 --> 00:05:53.122
-[bear groans]
-[Kiruko] Here, hurry up, come on!

00:05:53.206 --> 00:05:55.753
-[Maru panting]
-[Kiruko] Climb up now!

00:05:55.836 --> 00:05:57.130
[Maru] Please don't leave me!

00:05:57.214 --> 00:05:58.675
-[objects clatter]
-[both clamoring]

00:06:07.067 --> 00:06:08.402
[Kiruko sighs]

00:06:08.486 --> 00:06:11.701
Wow. My parkour skills are on point.

00:06:13.580 --> 00:06:14.582
[both gasp]

00:06:15.250 --> 00:06:17.087
[both] There's a freaking bear down there!

00:06:17.170 --> 00:06:19.676
You have no idea
how scary that was for me.

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:22.055
I thought I was just gonna do
the Maru Touch,

00:06:22.138 --> 00:06:24.686
but what I did was literally poke a bear.

00:06:24.769 --> 00:06:26.230
I saw death today.

00:06:26.313 --> 00:06:29.278
-I stared at it from this close!
-I'm so sorry!

00:06:29.361 --> 00:06:31.908
That guy told us it was a monster,
so I thought--

00:06:31.992 --> 00:06:33.912
It's not your fault, or that guy's fault.

00:06:33.996 --> 00:06:37.294
It basically is a monster. Look at it!

00:06:39.464 --> 00:06:41.511
I mean, yeah, it's huge and feral,
and hungry,

00:06:41.594 --> 00:06:44.642
but at least it can't climb ladders.
A gorilla would be way worse.

00:06:46.103 --> 00:06:47.480
[groans]

00:06:52.950 --> 00:06:54.494
[Kiruko] Amazing.

00:06:54.579 --> 00:06:56.206
It's gonna get cold soon.

00:06:57.042 --> 00:06:59.672
Oh, hey. Where did the bear go?

00:06:59.756 --> 00:07:03.387
It was circling the place like a big
furry buzzard, but now it's gone.

00:07:03.471 --> 00:07:04.891
Let's go before it comes back.

00:07:09.399 --> 00:07:12.405
I only have one round left
if the fourth shot works.

00:07:12.489 --> 00:07:15.495
-And do you think it's gonna?
-Um…

00:07:15.579 --> 00:07:17.165
I'll warm up the battery.

00:07:22.133 --> 00:07:24.387
-Uh-oh.
-"Uh-oh" what?

00:07:26.308 --> 00:07:29.356
So, bad news.

00:07:29.439 --> 00:07:30.567
I dropped the battery.

00:07:31.611 --> 00:07:33.532
But the good news is-- Uh--

00:07:34.116 --> 00:07:36.328
[crying] The good news is-- Uh--

00:07:36.411 --> 00:07:38.165
There is no good news, is there?

00:07:39.334 --> 00:07:42.006
Oh, come on. That is a long way down.

00:07:42.591 --> 00:07:44.469
-Go get it.
-Oh, yeah, right.

00:07:44.554 --> 00:07:46.306
What if that bear's
still hanging around somewhere?

00:07:48.352 --> 00:07:49.647
[Kiruko] Look at me, Maru.

00:07:49.730 --> 00:07:54.156
What do you see?
Am I a woman, or am I a man?

00:07:54.239 --> 00:07:55.324
What?

00:07:55.408 --> 00:07:56.911
Where did that come from?

00:07:56.995 --> 00:07:57.997
[Kiruko] Hmm?

00:07:59.750 --> 00:08:02.463
I mean, I'm sorry, dude,
but you look like a girl.

00:08:02.548 --> 00:08:06.096
Are you gonna tell me this was a test
and I've failed now, or what?

00:08:06.180 --> 00:08:07.182
[Kiruko exclaims]

00:08:07.766 --> 00:08:09.770
I'll let you touch my boobs
if you go get--

00:08:12.693 --> 00:08:13.820
