00:08:13.904 --> 00:08:15.866
Oh, my God, you are so stupid!

00:08:18.287 --> 00:08:20.082
-[chuckles]
-[sighs]

00:08:20.166 --> 00:08:21.460
[gasps] Look out!

00:08:21.502 --> 00:08:23.130
-[howling]
-It's back!

00:08:23.214 --> 00:08:25.468
[grunting]

00:08:27.472 --> 00:08:29.602
-[growling]
-[Maru groans]

00:08:33.067 --> 00:08:34.444
Damn thing was waiting for us.

00:08:35.238 --> 00:08:36.866
It definitely won't leave us alone.

00:08:37.450 --> 00:08:40.749
So either we just live here now,
or we try to kill it.

00:08:42.795 --> 00:08:45.592
[Kiruko] Yeah, about that…
I gotta tell ya,

00:08:45.676 --> 00:08:48.347
the only reason
I'm not bear chow right now

00:08:48.430 --> 00:08:50.434
is because
the adrenaline rush helped me climb.

00:08:50.936 --> 00:08:52.606
There's no way I can get back down.

00:08:53.608 --> 00:08:54.652
Sorry, what?

00:08:54.735 --> 00:08:58.409
Listen, normal people
aren't spider monkeys like you, okay?

00:08:58.492 --> 00:09:00.371
It's a miracle I even made it up here.

00:09:00.914 --> 00:09:02.333
So, here's the plan.

00:09:02.417 --> 00:09:03.712
You're gonna take the Kiru-Beam,

00:09:03.795 --> 00:09:07.135
shimmy on down there, and one-hit-KO
that bear in the face.

00:09:07.218 --> 00:09:10.099
Then I'll jump down and use the
bear's corpse to cushion my fall.

00:09:12.395 --> 00:09:16.613
Good news is, it's a regular animal.
All you need is one shot to the head.

00:09:17.615 --> 00:09:21.246
Okay, so props for creativity on your
plan, but one flaw.

00:09:21.330 --> 00:09:25.212
There's no freaking way I'll hit its head.
I can't shoot like you.

00:09:25.922 --> 00:09:28.135
Am I really that good of a shot?

00:09:28.218 --> 00:09:29.847
Are you being serious?

00:09:29.930 --> 00:09:33.354
I have seen you shoot a power pole
while climbing a fence,

00:09:33.437 --> 00:09:35.692
and wing a dude in the arm
while running away.

00:09:36.276 --> 00:09:38.447
So I'm-- I'm good at this?

00:09:38.531 --> 00:09:39.867
Well, yeah. Of course you are.

00:09:39.950 --> 00:09:42.080
I would have died at least five times
already without you.

00:09:46.046 --> 00:09:47.048
What's wrong?

00:09:49.845 --> 00:09:51.473
You think I'm good?

00:09:52.141 --> 00:09:53.978
[Haruki] <i>I'll be okay,</i>
<i>I have my gun, remember?</i>

00:09:54.062 --> 00:09:55.774
[Robin] <i>Did you think</i>
<i>I was playing around?</i>

00:09:55.857 --> 00:09:57.485
<i>When I tell you to stay put, you do it!</i>

00:09:57.569 --> 00:09:59.322
[Haruki] <i>It's plenty of time.</i>
<i>I've got this.</i>

00:10:02.161 --> 00:10:03.455
-[Kiruko] Okay.
-Hmm?

00:10:04.082 --> 00:10:05.752
We're gonna make a new plan.

00:10:08.591 --> 00:10:12.558
<i>First, we'll get ourselves warmed up,</i>
<i>while we wait for the bear to wander away.</i>

00:10:13.601 --> 00:10:16.231
-[Maru] <i>And once it does?</i>
-<i>That's where you come in.</i>

00:10:16.314 --> 00:10:17.943
<i>Climb down while it's distracted.</i>

00:10:19.028 --> 00:10:20.156
[groans]

00:10:21.324 --> 00:10:24.080
[Kiruko] <i>As soon as you land,</i>
<i>it's trust fall time for me.</i>

00:10:28.213 --> 00:10:29.759
[whimpers, screams]

00:10:33.390 --> 00:10:36.731
<i>After you catch me,</i>
<i>run away as fast as you can.</i>

00:10:37.608 --> 00:10:40.154
[Maru] <i>What about you?</i>
<i>What if the fourth shot won't fire?</i>

00:10:40.864 --> 00:10:42.576
[growling]

00:10:44.037 --> 00:10:46.166
[Kiruko] <i>If that happens…</i>

00:10:48.253 --> 00:10:50.801
<i>Then I'll make sure to hold it off</i>
<i>until you get away.</i>

00:10:58.148 --> 00:10:59.275
[squelching]

00:11:05.789 --> 00:11:08.335
[sighs deeply]

00:11:09.755 --> 00:11:13.178
[panting]

00:11:16.978 --> 00:11:19.692
[gasps] Why the hell didn't you run away?

00:11:21.361 --> 00:11:23.783
Did you seriously think
I'd follow your terrible plan,

00:11:23.867 --> 00:11:25.871
and just let a bear maul you to death?

00:11:25.954 --> 00:11:26.956
That hurts, man.

00:11:28.793 --> 00:11:31.757
[chuckles] You underestimate me.

00:11:31.841 --> 00:11:34.262
I knew the shot would go off
the whole time.

00:11:34.345 --> 00:11:35.557
Yeah?

00:11:36.517 --> 00:11:39.565
The battery had the power
of your horny energy.

00:11:39.648 --> 00:11:42.821
-It was your idea. You can't pick on me.
-[laughs]

00:11:42.905 --> 00:11:45.117
-Sis, stop it!
-[Kiruko laughing]

00:11:47.079 --> 00:11:49.459
[bystander 1] Iwata! Come on, wake up!

00:11:49.543 --> 00:11:50.587
Iwata!

00:11:51.505 --> 00:11:54.344
-[Totori] Iwata…
-[bystander 2] Shimomoto didn't make it.

00:11:54.427 --> 00:11:55.555
-[bystander 3] Totori.
-Huh?

00:11:56.264 --> 00:11:58.477
Tell me about the people
who brought him here.

00:11:59.187 --> 00:12:01.441
They just said their names
were of no importance,

00:12:01.525 --> 00:12:02.819
and were gone on the breeze.

00:12:02.903 --> 00:12:05.742
-[bystander 1] Seriously?
-Who the hell were they?

00:12:05.825 --> 00:12:07.537
They took that bear on all alone?

00:12:09.332 --> 00:12:12.463
-I was hoping to meet them.
-[bystander 2] Same here.

00:12:12.547 --> 00:12:14.425
[bystander 3] Since when do bears
even live here, anyway?

00:12:14.510 --> 00:12:16.054
Man, I love animals.

00:12:16.973 --> 00:12:19.268
Their bodies don't disappear,
and we can eat them.

00:12:20.605 --> 00:12:21.774
Okay, Maru.

00:12:21.857 --> 00:12:24.362
I got tricked back there,
and I'm gonna tell you how.

00:12:24.445 --> 00:12:25.782
Wait, we got tricked?

00:12:26.366 --> 00:12:28.997
You know those vigilantes
we met in the tent city?

00:12:31.459 --> 00:12:34.633
Well, they're bandits,
and they lured us right into a trap.

00:12:35.342 --> 00:12:37.346
How could those guys have lured us?

00:12:37.430 --> 00:12:39.727
100% safe water?

00:12:39.810 --> 00:12:41.689
-[Maru] <i>Oh.</i>
-<i>Yeah.</i>

00:12:41.772 --> 00:12:44.945
<i>I bet their plan was to block the entrance</i>
<i>to that underground passage</i>

00:12:45.029 --> 00:12:46.239
<i>once we got close.</i>

00:12:46.824 --> 00:12:49.203
The map-seller was definitely
in on it too.

00:12:49.705 --> 00:12:53.253
Are you saying the whole map
is useless lies we can't trust, then?

00:12:53.336 --> 00:12:56.176
I assume some of it's real, but who knows?

00:12:56.259 --> 00:12:59.600
That's enough regret for now.
Let's get some rest.

00:13:00.184 --> 00:13:02.856
I know we didn't plan on staying,
but we're here now.

00:13:04.025 --> 00:13:07.574
Maru, aren't you gonna go to your room?
You know, she gave us two.

00:13:07.657 --> 00:13:09.243
I'll see you in the morning.

00:13:10.370 --> 00:13:12.500
[Maru]
Isn't there something you're forgetting?

00:13:12.584 --> 00:13:14.045
[Kiruko] Huh?

00:13:14.128 --> 00:13:18.805
You and I had a deal.
And I made good on my end of it, Sis.

00:13:21.059 --> 00:13:24.107
-[Kiruko] Uh…
-I put my life on the line.

00:13:26.277 --> 00:13:28.281
Time to let me touch your boobs.

00:13:32.456 --> 00:13:35.505
[Kiruko] <i>My sister's hair used to be</i>
<i>straight and black.</i>

00:13:36.549 --> 00:13:40.682
<i>Apparently, sometimes your hair can change</i>
<i>after you get injured</i>

00:13:40.765 --> 00:13:42.894
<i>or you go through a major stress.</i>

00:13:42.978 --> 00:13:46.694
