I started growing this dry, red hair,

00:13:46.777 --> 00:13:48.865
that looks nothing like hers used to.

00:13:49.448 --> 00:13:52.204
But I think it's a warning from my sister:

00:13:53.123 --> 00:13:55.168
"You'd better not mess with my body."

00:13:55.670 --> 00:13:56.881
Know what I mean?

00:13:56.964 --> 00:13:58.425
[Maru] Cool story.

00:13:59.176 --> 00:14:00.763
Now take off your jacket.

00:14:02.601 --> 00:14:04.312
I mean, it's your call, dude.

00:14:04.395 --> 00:14:06.984
Just remember that
this is whose boobs you're touching.

00:14:07.067 --> 00:14:08.153
This guy right here.

00:14:08.236 --> 00:14:09.865
But as long as you're cool with that,

00:14:09.948 --> 00:14:13.371
I'll hold up my end of the deal as a man
'cause that's what men do.

00:14:13.455 --> 00:14:14.750
So keep that in mind.

00:14:14.833 --> 00:14:17.547
-[Maru grunts]
-[Kiruko squeals] Whoa!

00:14:17.631 --> 00:14:20.637
[Kiruko] Okay, let's set some
ground rules first, all right?

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:22.724
Like how many seconds you-- [screams]

00:14:23.517 --> 00:14:25.354
[both]
<i>Well, that sure sounded like a girl.</i>

00:14:25.437 --> 00:14:26.607
[door opens]

00:14:27.232 --> 00:14:28.694
Hey, lovebirds.

00:14:37.086 --> 00:14:40.510
What part of "the cleanest futons in town"
don't you understand?

00:14:41.386 --> 00:14:43.264
-Come on, perv. Let's go.
-Wait!

00:14:44.851 --> 00:14:47.022
[whimpering]

00:14:47.607 --> 00:14:48.818
Now that that's done,

00:14:50.697 --> 00:14:52.909
how about you give me a try?

00:14:55.414 --> 00:15:00.257
800K, or you can fork over
your solar-powered light. What do you say?

00:15:00.340 --> 00:15:02.929
