00:15:03.013 --> 00:15:05.392
Well, yeah. But I didn't take anything.

00:15:05.475 --> 00:15:07.271
So, what's your deal?

00:15:07.354 --> 00:15:10.068
Want me to keep
the bandana on during or no?

00:15:10.152 --> 00:15:13.826
Oh, my name's Totori, by the way.
I don't know my last name.

00:15:13.909 --> 00:15:17.416
[stammering] No… Bad--
Thanks, but no thanks to all of this.

00:15:17.499 --> 00:15:20.506
For your information,
I like older girls and-- [gasps]

00:15:21.090 --> 00:15:23.303
-Oh.
-[giggles]

00:15:23.929 --> 00:15:25.307
[heart beating]

00:15:32.697 --> 00:15:34.158
-[Maru gasps]
-[Totori shrieks]

00:15:34.910 --> 00:15:36.162
Are you a--

00:15:36.245 --> 00:15:38.709
Hey, Sis! Get in here now!

00:15:38.793 --> 00:15:40.295
[Totori] Ugh! What are you doing?

00:15:40.378 --> 00:15:43.176
-Get off!
-[Maru] Stay still. Don't move.

00:15:43.259 --> 00:15:45.347
-Hurry up, Sis!
-Hey! What's the matter?

00:15:45.430 --> 00:15:48.103
-Sis, I got in!
-Ow, that hurts. Stop it.

00:15:50.900 --> 00:15:53.614
You got in where?

00:15:53.697 --> 00:15:55.827
[gasps]

00:16:00.711 --> 00:16:02.799
What the hell have you done?

00:16:03.801 --> 00:16:04.803
No…

00:16:05.847 --> 00:16:09.019
[narrator] <i>Maru realized that</i>
<i>no explanation would ever be enough</i>

00:16:09.103 --> 00:16:11.399
<i>to save him from this humiliation.</i>

00:16:11.482 --> 00:16:15.323
<i>The misunderstanding was as deep and dark</i>
<i>as the gaping pit of despair</i>

00:16:15.407 --> 00:16:16.827
<i>that swallowed his soul.</i>

00:16:18.622 --> 00:16:20.918
[medical robot]
<i>No illnesses have been detected.</i>

00:16:22.212 --> 00:16:25.177
So, there's nothing wrong? What a relief.

00:16:25.803 --> 00:16:28.308
<i>Your body is showing signs of fatigue.</i>

00:16:28.391 --> 00:16:30.187
<i>A nap is advised at this time.</i>

00:16:30.270 --> 00:16:32.191
[students chattering]

00:16:41.668 --> 00:16:42.670
[gasps]

00:16:45.718 --> 00:16:46.970
Who's there?

00:16:49.141 --> 00:16:51.062
Uh… Wait, what?

00:16:55.655 --> 00:16:57.575
[gasps, screams]

00:16:58.076 --> 00:16:59.913
[breathing heavily]

00:17:01.249 --> 00:17:02.334
A-Asura?

00:17:05.340 --> 00:17:08.054
What are you good at, Tokio?

00:17:10.350 --> 00:17:11.728
[Tokio] What do you mean?

00:17:17.740 --> 00:17:18.742
Where'd you go?

00:17:20.078 --> 00:17:21.289
[gasps]

00:17:22.792 --> 00:17:25.923
[shrieks] No! What's happening to me?

00:17:26.007 --> 00:17:27.802
Doctor, help me!

00:17:28.595 --> 00:17:29.597
Doctor!

00:17:31.727 --> 00:17:32.770
[gasps]

00:17:36.653 --> 00:17:37.655
A dream?

00:17:38.156 --> 00:17:39.868
[sighs, whimpers]

00:17:42.372 --> 00:17:43.792
So, how are you feeling?

00:17:44.335 --> 00:17:46.130
[Tokio] Uh, o-okay, I think.

00:17:49.554 --> 00:17:50.556
Hmm.

00:17:51.642 --> 00:17:54.063
We are so sorry again.

00:17:54.564 --> 00:17:56.275
[Maru] This place is my heaven now.

00:17:56.359 --> 00:17:59.741
I promise I'll spend the rest of my life
trying to earn your forgiveness.

00:17:59.824 --> 00:18:01.077
Oh, my.

00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:03.999
This is fun,
but the groveling is kind of a lot.

00:18:04.083 --> 00:18:06.212
-You can get up already. Come on.
-[both sigh]

00:18:06.295 --> 00:18:08.257
This guy didn't do anything wrong.

00:18:08.341 --> 00:18:10.053
I swear, the whole thing was my idea.

00:18:10.136 --> 00:18:13.101
Thank you so much.

00:18:13.727 --> 00:18:15.815
[Totori]
I mean, you can ask about my past,

00:18:16.566 --> 00:18:18.319
but I'm just a typical orphan.

00:18:18.946 --> 00:18:20.700
You know, I don't even remember a time

00:18:20.783 --> 00:18:23.079
it wasn't just me and the vigilantes
out here.

00:18:23.664 --> 00:18:27.212
You were born after the Great Disaster
and raised by strangers?

00:18:27.295 --> 00:18:29.843
So then your parents might be alive
out there somewhere.

00:18:30.636 --> 00:18:33.391
Well, it's not like meeting them
would do me any good.

00:18:34.143 --> 00:18:36.982
For me, it's all about what's profitable.

00:18:37.065 --> 00:18:39.445
And anything that feels good
makes you a lot of money.

00:18:40.196 --> 00:18:43.327
First, I'm gonna rent out
more and more clean rooms and futons.

00:18:43.411 --> 00:18:46.668
Then, I'm gonna have a whole bunch of sex
with the customers who aren't skeezy.

00:18:46.752 --> 00:18:49.298
And then I'm gonna be the King of Hotels!

00:18:52.429 --> 00:18:55.561
[Maru] I don't get how I was able to
go into a human like that.

00:18:55.644 --> 00:18:58.776
I mean, I'm glad that
everything got cleared up but still.

00:19:00.195 --> 00:19:04.036
I thought I was gonna have to kill her
with the Maru-Touch to prove it happened.

00:19:04.119 --> 00:19:06.248
I was really freaked out
for a minute there.

00:19:06.332 --> 00:19:07.543
Hold up.

00:19:07.627 --> 00:19:09.379
What happened to the Failure Dive?

00:19:09.463 --> 00:19:11.551
See, I knew you were gonna rub that in.

00:19:11.635 --> 00:19:14.682
As soon as I said it, I thought,
"Sis won't let that go."

00:19:14.766 --> 00:19:15.768
And I was right.

00:19:15.851 --> 00:19:17.647
[Kiruko] Oh, now I remember.

00:19:17.730 --> 00:19:18.899
Fatal Dive!

00:19:18.982 --> 00:19:20.653
[Maru sobbing] Leave me alone!

00:19:22.990 --> 00:19:24.201
[broom sweeping]

00:19:24.284 --> 00:19:26.247
[Kiruko] Well, see you.

00:19:26.330 --> 00:19:28.627
Those futons were really comfy.

00:19:29.169 --> 00:19:31.340
Where's all that energy
you had last night?

00:19:31.423 --> 00:19:33.427
You're looking kinda rough today.

00:19:34.597 --> 00:19:36.768
I heard the boss died.

00:19:36.852 --> 00:19:39.899
-[Maru gasps]
-It happened early this morning.

00:19:40.568 --> 00:19:43.281
You guys saved him but he's still…

00:19:43.991 --> 00:19:47.790
He was always so strong,
and I didn't even think he could die.

00:19:49.251 --> 00:19:52.299
He was always a really good boss to us,
you know?

00:19:53.426 --> 00:19:56.975
But it's fine. Death's just part of life.
[sniffles]

00:20:01.442 --> 00:20:02.862
[Kiruko] Wanna come with us?

00:20:04.489 --> 00:20:05.491
Hmm.

00:20:06.410 --> 00:20:07.580
Mm-mmm.

00:20:08.164 --> 00:20:09.166
[Kiruko] Okay.

00:20:14.259 --> 00:20:16.765
Do it! Become the King of Hotels.

00:20:23.695 --> 00:20:27.703
I guess even a guy like that
can end up with people who care about him.

00:20:29.540 --> 00:20:32.505
You know,
if I was born and raised in this area,

00:20:33.799 --> 00:20:35.552
I might have been one of his crew.

00:22:39.382 --> 00:22:41.220
You're looking a lot better
than last time.

00:22:41.804 --> 00:22:45.394
I was just worried about something.
But I'm great now.

00:22:45.896 --> 00:22:47.023
I'm glad.

00:22:57.335 --> 00:22:59.297
DETECTING DETAILED POINTS

00:23:03.264 --> 00:23:05.644
So I was right. This is it.

00:23:06.688 --> 00:23:09.484
There's only one person
that footprint could have belonged to.

00:23:09.568 --> 00:23:11.071
And it's Tokio.

00:23:12.323 --> 00:23:14.912
But how? Without anyone noticing?

00:23:17.458 --> 00:23:21.509
[Tokio] I know how this sounds,
but I saw Asura's ghost today.

00:23:21.592 --> 00:23:23.555
-Really?
-Maybe.

00:23:23.638 --> 00:23:25.308
It might have been a dream.

00:23:26.226 --> 00:23:28.606
You liked Asura a lot, didn't you?

00:23:29.441 --> 00:23:30.443
Yeah.

00:23:32.573 --> 00:23:33.575
I did.

00:23:33.658 --> 00:23:36.956
But it was a different kind of love
than the love I feel for you.

00:23:37.791 --> 00:23:38.793
You know that, right?

00:23:42.091 --> 00:23:43.093
[giggles]

